<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idc31d86d7-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87" identifier="/us/usc/t38/s1940"><num value="1940">§ 1940.</num><heading> Definition</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">For the purposes of this subchapter, the term “insurance” means United States Government life insurance.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idc31d86d8-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87">(<ref href="/us/pl/85/857">Pub. L. 85–857</ref>, <date date="1958-09-02">Sept. 2, 1958</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/72/1158">72 Stat. 1158</ref>, § 740; renumbered § 1940, <ref href="/us/pl/102/83/s5/a">Pub. L. 102–83, § 5(a)</ref>, <date date="1991-08-06">Aug. 6, 1991</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/105/406">105 Stat. 406</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
